# Build artefacts
# Anchored to the repo root so the line ignores ONLY the built binary,
# not the cmd/cohort-walker/ source directory (an unanchored "cohort-walker"
# pattern matches a path component at any depth and would shadow the CLI).
/cohort-walker
/cohort-walker.exe
*.test
*.out

